article.headline: Dancier's 16 lead Le Moyne over UT Martin 65-53
article.description: — AJ Dancier had 16 points in Le Moyne's 65-53 victory against UT Martin on Friday night.
article.linkText: Dancier's 16 lead Le Moyne over UT Martin 65-53
article.story: CORPUS CHRISTI, Texas -- — AJ Dancier had 16 points in Le Moyne's 65-53 victory against UT Martin on Friday night. Dancier shot 4 for 10 (3 for 6 from 3-point range) and 5 of 5 from the free-throw line for the Dolphins (2-4). Ocypher Owens added 11 points while going 3 of 9 from the floor, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and 4 for 4 from the line while he also had nine rebounds and three blocks. Dwayne Koroma shot 5 of 7 from the field and 1 of 5 from the free-throw line to finish with 11 points, while adding eight rebounds and three steals. Afan Trnka finished with 12 points for the Skyhawks (2-4). Tarence Guinyard added 10 points for UT Martin. Lamine Niang also had eight points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
